<h2>Hello admin,</h2>

<h4>You have a new evaluator applicant, their information is below.</h4>
<p>
      Name: <%= @applicant[:first_name] %> <%= @applicant[:last_name] %>
  <br>Email: <%= @applicant[:email] %>
  <br>Phone: <%= @applicant[:phone_number] %>
  <br>Skype: <%= @applicant[:skype] %>
  <br>Gender: <%= @applicant[:gender] %>
  <br>Address: <%= @applicant[:address] %> <%= @applicant[:city] %>, <%= @applicant[:state] %> <%= @applicant[:zip] %>
  <br>Birthday: <%= @applicant[:birthday] %>
  <br>Education: <%= @applicant[:education] %>
  <br>Employment: <%= @applicant[:employment] %>
  <br>Occupation: <%= @applicant[:occupation] %>
  <br>Certification: <%= @applicant[:certification] %>
  <br>Qualifications: <%= @applicant[:qualifications] %>
  <br>Where they found us: <%= @applicant[:found_us_by] %>
  <br>Do they work with any other secret shopper companies: <%= @applicant[:work_with_other_companies] %>
</p>
<br>
<h4>Questions</h4>
<p>
  <br><br><i>Please describe in 80 characters as to why you would be a good evaluator.</i> - <strong><%= @applicant[:writing] %></strong>
  <br><br><i>Have you worked in a restaurant, and if so please explain what position(s) you held.</i> - <strong><%= @applicant[:restaurant_experience] %></strong>
  <br><br><i>How often can you service evaluations in your home area?</i> - <strong><%= @applicant[:availability] %></strong>
  <br><br><i>List the cities you frequent for dining.</i> - <strong><%= @applicant[:other_locations] %></strong>
  <br><br><i>Please list the following words in reverse alphabetical order: 'alligator', 'orange', 'label', 'yams', 'orangutan'?</i> - <strong><%= @applicant[:literacy] %></strong>
  <br><br><i>Lets say you just finished dinner at a restaurant you are evaluating. You get home and can't remember the concierge's name. What do you do?</i> - <strong><%= @applicant[:no_name_scenario] %></strong>
  <br><br><i>Where would you take a friend, if they where visiting your home town?</i> - <strong><%= @applicant[:good_time] %></strong>
  <br><br><i>What is your favorite all time restaurant?</i> - <strong><%= @applicant[:favorite_restaurant] %></strong>
  <br><br><i>Why is it your favorite?</i> - <strong><%= @applicant[:favorite_restaurant_why] %></strong>
</p>

<p>
  <br>
  <a href="<%= base_url %>/users/<%= @user.id %>/accept_application" target="_blank">Accept Applicant</a>.
  <a href="<%= base_url %>/users/<%= @user.id %>/decline_application" target="_blank">Deny Applicant</a>.
  (Note: If you receive a 404 page, this means you are not logged in as an admin.  Click the icon in the
  top right corner of the page, logout if necessary, type in your admin credentials into the login, then hit the submit button.)

  <br><br>
  Please do not send this email to anyone.
</p>